    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075510/extras/c2b7970218f80a966994b041f6e12a38.poster.avif?t=1763458151\" width=620 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075510/extras/c2b7970218f80a966994b041f6e12a38.webm?t=1763458151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075510/extras/c2b7970218f80a966994b041f6e12a38.mp4?t=1763458151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《爱心：神女之爱》是一款以中国古代神话为背景的短篇视觉小说，讲述神女与战士相遇后，二人命运交织的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爱心是纯洁无瑕的年轻神女，至善至美的化身。而温杨则是位身经百战的战士，过往的伤痕深深烙印在他身上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场意外化作试炼，迫使两人质疑亘古不变的真理：责任与情感孰轻孰重？爱能否赎清罪孽？一切信念崩塌之后，又将剩下什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2075510/extras/215fbfde8f6b16fa0c806e691a91bcc2.avif?t=1763458151\" width=620 height=113 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >短篇叙事游戏（英文原文约6800字）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双结局，但只有一处极为关键的选择会决定故事的结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心打造的视听氛围，极致烘托戏剧张力</p></li></ul>",
